%p Thanks for submitting your response to this fact checking request:

.fact_check_request
  .details
    %span.from= @fact_check_request.email_address
    on
    %span.time= @fact_check_request.updated_at.to_s(:long_ordinal)
  .comments= format_in_paragraphs @fact_check_request.comments

%p The policy is show below

.policy
  %h1.title= @edition.title
  %div.body
    = @edition.body.split("\n\n").collect{|paragraph| "<p>#{paragraph}</p>" }.join.html_safe
  %p.written_by
    Written by
    %span.author= @edition.author.name